1
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:41,070
[The Demon Hunter's Romance]

2
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:43,910
[Episode 27]

3
00:01:49,070 --> 00:01:49,680
I lost.

4
00:01:50,479 --> 00:01:51,920
Your Go skills are impressive.

5
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,450
Better than your father's.

6
00:01:53,789 --> 00:01:54,920
To be honest, Uncle,

7
00:01:55,150 --> 00:01:56,479
when I was at home before,

8
00:01:56,479 --> 00:01:58,740
my father didn't dare to play against me.

9
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:02,200
Banxia.

10
00:02:03,070 --> 00:02:03,800
You're back.

11
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,180
I need your help with something.

12
00:02:06,180 --> 00:02:07,240
What is it? Tell me.

13
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,590
It's getting into autumn these days.

14
00:02:11,590 --> 00:02:12,910
The weather is turning cooler.

15
00:02:12,910 --> 00:02:15,170
I want to buy some fabric to make clothes.

16
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,560
But the East Market is too far.

17
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,890
I don't have a carriage.

18
00:02:18,150 --> 00:02:18,800
That's simple.

19
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,710
My carriage is right outside.

20
00:02:19,710 --> 00:02:20,430
I'll take you there.

21
00:02:20,430 --> 00:02:20,730
Let's go.

22
00:02:20,730 --> 00:02:21,190
Wait.

23
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,020
Banxia.

24
00:02:23,430 --> 00:02:24,430
It's time for dinner.

25
00:02:24,430 --> 00:02:25,590
If you need to buy something,

26
00:02:25,590 --> 00:02:26,790
go tomorrow instead.

27
00:02:26,820 --> 00:02:28,500
No, I must go today.

28
00:02:31,140 --> 00:02:32,000
Father, if you think

29
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,730
you'll have no one to dine with,

30
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,680
you can go next door to find Physician Jiu.

31
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:37,120
After all, he rendered great help to you.

32
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,850
It's good for you to get closer.

33
00:02:38,910 --> 00:02:39,710
That's right.

34
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:40,840
Xuanye is easygoing.

35
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,030
He's easy to get along with.

36
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,240
You're neighbors.

37
00:02:43,870 --> 00:02:45,870
It's good to visit each other often.

38
00:02:49,870 --> 00:02:50,590
Well then...

39
00:02:50,590 --> 00:02:51,000
Let's go.

40
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,329
Okay.

41
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:54,750
Young Master,

42
00:02:54,750 --> 00:02:55,430
where do you want to go?

43
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:56,400
To the East Market.

44
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,560
To buy fabric with Banxia.

45
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:57,960
Got it.

46
00:02:58,710 --> 00:02:59,960
It's just to buy fabric.

47
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:02,560
We don't need others to keep us company, right?

48
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:04,800
Can you drive the carriage?

49
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,400
Yes, I can.

50
00:03:05,540 --> 00:03:07,070
Then let's go by ourselves.

51
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,890
Of course, that's fine.

52
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,910
You wait here.

53
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:12,430
Got it.

54
00:03:12,710 --> 00:03:13,170
Banxia.

55
00:03:26,050 --> 00:03:26,680
Banxia.

56
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:29,430
Xuanye.

57
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:34,690
Are we going or not?

58
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:36,060
We're leaving now.

59
00:03:36,060 --> 00:03:37,260
Let's catch up later.

60
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,150
Xuanye.

61
00:03:55,890 --> 00:03:56,680
Do you know what's going on

62
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,940
with Banxia recently?

63
00:03:58,030 --> 00:03:59,070
She's ignoring me

64
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:00,360
and doesn't invite me to her house

65
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,090
to eat delicious food anymore.

66
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:06,080
That Mr. Li just now,

67
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,190
he said before

68
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:08,750
that he's Banxia's fiancé.

69
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:10,560
Xuanye,

70
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,360
I thought you two

71
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,240
were a couple.

72
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:17,720
Well, if Banxia

73
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:19,040
marries someone else,

74
00:04:19,230 --> 00:04:20,089
does that mean I won't be able to eat

75
00:04:20,089 --> 00:04:20,950
the delicious food she makes anymore?

76
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:22,150
Stop talking so much.

77
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,050
Get back to work.

78
00:04:47,870 --> 00:04:48,430
Xuanye,

79
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,530
are you sure this will work?

80
00:04:51,870 --> 00:04:53,470
We'll only know after we try.

81
00:04:54,010 --> 00:04:55,480
After all, this is just a formula

82
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,490
guessed by smell.

83
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,130
I'm not certain either.

84
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,480
These are all the things

85
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,140
I smelled at his place before.

86
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,000
Perhaps this is the

87
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,330
key to this magic spell.

88
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:07,430
What kind of magic spell is this?

89
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:08,430
It's so powerful.

90
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,120
I heard before

91
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:12,760
that some demons

92
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,820
can use secret techniques

93
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,580
to share others' five senses.

94
00:05:17,370 --> 00:05:19,070
But as to exchanging five senses

95
00:05:19,070 --> 00:05:21,040
and controlling the other's body like this,

96
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,970
this is the first time I've seen it.

97
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,270
Let's give it a try.

98
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:26,800
We can't let him

99
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,270
lead us by the nose anymore.

100
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:28,730
Chi Xue,

101
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:30,240
help me set up a formation in a moment.

102
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:30,570
Okay.

103
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:32,230
[Heal and Help]

104
00:05:58,830 --> 00:06:02,390
Jia corresponds to Zhen (the East), and Yi corresponds to Li (the South).

105
00:06:02,390 --> 00:06:04,390
All spirits return to their origin.

106
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,240
Go!

107
00:07:22,780 --> 00:07:23,370
Xuanye?

108
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,360
Who are you?

109
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,050
Who exactly are you?

110
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:41,980
If you don't speak,

111
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:44,170
don't blame me for being impolite!

112
00:07:45,860 --> 00:07:46,790
You? Seriously?

113
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,490
What are you doing?

114
00:08:28,270 --> 00:08:28,870
Leave now.

115
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,080
I said leave.

116
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,020
Physician Jiu?

117
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:35,039
I've set up a formation

118
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:36,710
and switched identities with him.

119
00:08:36,710 --> 00:08:37,630
Time is limited.

120
00:08:37,630 --> 00:08:38,830
You need to leave now.

121
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,200
Leave.

122
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,070
Xuanye,

123
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,260
come back quickly.

124
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:18,730
I can't hold on anymore.

125
00:09:36,870 --> 00:09:37,440
Xuanye.

126
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,000
Chi Xue,

127
00:09:40,710 --> 00:09:41,510
what's wrong?

128
00:10:19,390 --> 00:10:19,870
Xuanye.

129
00:10:20,630 --> 00:10:22,630
That demon refused to say anything.

130
00:10:23,180 --> 00:10:24,150
In the Hundred Demon Catalog,

131
00:10:24,150 --> 00:10:26,150
there's no relevant record either.

132
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:27,790
However, I can sense that

133
00:10:28,110 --> 00:10:30,440
this demon's cultivation is not shallow.

134
00:10:31,750 --> 00:10:32,610
Is he dead then?

135
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:33,670
I sealed

136
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:35,600
the eight major acupoints in his body.

137
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,120
If he forcibly breaks through,

138
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,720
he will be severely injured.

139
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,480
Moreover, before I left,

140
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,550
I had set a big fire.

141
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,720
It's unlikely he can escape.

142
00:10:43,830 --> 00:10:45,090
It's still not secure.

143
00:10:45,510 --> 00:10:47,840
You should have killed him with one sword strike.

144
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,900
Our spiritual senses were connected at that time.

145
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:50,720
If I had killed him,

146
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:52,580
I wouldn't have survived either.

147
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,600
There was too little time.

148
00:11:01,650 --> 00:11:02,920
Then why don't we strike while the iron is hot

149
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:03,720
and try again?

150
00:11:04,580 --> 00:11:05,450
This magic spell

151
00:11:05,450 --> 00:11:07,260
consumed a lot of energy.

152
00:11:07,510 --> 00:11:09,240
I'm afraid of being backfired.

153
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:10,100
Besides, now,

154
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:11,230
he must be prepared.

155
00:11:11,830 --> 00:11:13,630
If we rashly try again,

156
00:11:14,060 --> 00:11:14,670
it's also possible that

157
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:16,070
we'll fall into his trap.

158
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:19,170
I wonder

159
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,530
if Banxia has returned.

160
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,820
Why are you mentioning her again?

161
00:11:24,870 --> 00:11:26,000
Because I'm hungry.

162
00:11:26,150 --> 00:11:27,790
I haven't eaten anything today.

163
00:11:27,790 --> 00:11:29,290
I just confronted that demon for a long time.

164
00:11:29,290 --> 00:11:30,250
I'm starving.

165
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,890
Aren't steamed buns filling enough?

166
00:11:32,890 --> 00:11:34,150
They don't taste good.

167
00:11:34,220 --> 00:11:34,820
I'm upset.

168
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,300
Where has she gone?

169
00:11:45,220 --> 00:11:46,060
What did she

170
00:11:46,510 --> 00:11:47,820
buy today anyway?

171
00:11:50,860 --> 00:11:52,260
Let me tell you secretly.

172
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:53,810
She told me not to tell.

173
00:11:54,590 --> 00:11:56,250
She bought hypostasis water.

174
00:11:57,870 --> 00:11:59,510
What does she need hypostasis water for?

175
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:00,580
She doesn't even know how to use it.

176
00:12:00,580 --> 00:12:01,550
She knows how to use it.

177
00:12:01,550 --> 00:12:03,210
I taught her the incantation.

178
00:12:04,150 --> 00:12:06,880
How could there be any problem with what I taught?

179
00:12:19,030 --> 00:12:19,620
Banxia.

180
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:23,850
Aren't we supposed to go to the East Market to buy fabric?

181
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:24,910
Why are we here?

182
00:12:26,510 --> 00:12:27,100
I

183
00:12:27,750 --> 00:12:29,410
feel dizzy because of hunger.

184
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:31,550
And if we don't head back soon,

185
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:34,200
it'll be dark by the time we get back.

186
00:12:35,150 --> 00:12:35,790
How about

187
00:12:36,030 --> 00:12:36,610
we leave?

188
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:39,130
Wait a little longer. A little longer.

189
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:40,350
Just a little longer.

190
00:12:44,670 --> 00:12:46,170
When my father talked about the arrangements for our marriage,

191
00:12:46,170 --> 00:12:47,120
did he explain

192
00:12:47,150 --> 00:12:48,750
my situation to you clearly?

193
00:12:49,550 --> 00:12:50,810
He told us everything.

194
00:12:51,300 --> 00:12:52,300
Your father said,

195
00:12:53,270 --> 00:12:54,960
you're well-behaved, sensible,

196
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:56,220
gentle, and virtuous.

197
00:12:56,510 --> 00:12:58,280
Although you're only two years younger than I am,

198
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:59,200
you've read

199
00:12:59,230 --> 00:13:00,760
just as many books as I have.

200
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,910
He even had our Four Pillars of Destiny compared

201
00:13:02,910 --> 00:13:03,440
and said

202
00:13:03,740 --> 00:13:04,400
the two of us

203
00:13:04,750 --> 00:13:05,950
are very compatible,

204
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,460
a match made in heaven.

205
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:08,790
He also said

206
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,540
that after we're married,

207
00:13:11,630 --> 00:13:13,670
we'll surely live in harmony

208
00:13:14,150 --> 00:13:15,410
and grow old together.

209
00:13:16,620 --> 00:13:17,980
That's not what I mean.

210
00:13:21,750 --> 00:13:22,630
My left eye...

211
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:25,730
You... You mean your hysteria?

212
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:28,100
Your father mentioned that, too.

213
00:13:28,870 --> 00:13:29,440
Well,

214
00:13:29,510 --> 00:13:30,770
doesn't it bother you?

215
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:33,320
I'm not that old-fashioned.

216
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:34,910
Everyone gets sick

217
00:13:35,150 --> 00:13:36,670
at some point in their life.

218
00:13:36,670 --> 00:13:37,180
This isn't something

219
00:13:37,180 --> 00:13:38,040
we can control.

220
00:13:38,940 --> 00:13:40,270
Of course, I understand

221
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,630
that as a young lady,

222
00:13:41,740 --> 00:13:43,000
you have many burdens.

223
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,290
But don't worry.

224
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:45,820
I will take good care of you.

225
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:47,620
And I will never look down on you.

226
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,890
It's not an illness.

227
00:13:50,550 --> 00:13:51,120
It's not.

228
00:13:51,390 --> 00:13:52,320
Absolutely not.

229
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:54,630
The things I see are real.

230
00:13:54,630 --> 00:13:56,550
There are really demons in this world.

231
00:13:56,550 --> 00:13:58,330
Think carefully, how can someone

232
00:13:58,330 --> 00:13:59,660
come back from the dead?

233
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:00,380
My father and the others

234
00:14:00,380 --> 00:14:01,860
were kidnapped by demons.

235
00:14:02,790 --> 00:14:04,720
I chased them all the way from Nanyang to Guangping.

236
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:06,000
Although I had help from a master,

237
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:07,390
it still took a tremendous effort

238
00:14:07,390 --> 00:14:08,550
to rescue them.

239
00:14:08,910 --> 00:14:09,390
This kind of thing,

240
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:10,720
if it happens once, it can happen again.

241
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:12,240
It may happen repeatedly.

242
00:14:12,510 --> 00:14:13,870
If we're married later,

243
00:14:14,030 --> 00:14:15,240
aren't you afraid that one day,

244
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:17,170
those demons might kidnap you too?

245
00:14:18,910 --> 00:14:20,840
They told me a few days ago

246
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:23,150
that your condition had greatly improved.

247
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:24,550
Has it relapsed?

248
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:27,600
But it doesn't matter.

249
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,600
My word is my bond.

250
00:14:28,900 --> 00:14:30,270
I'm willing to face this with you.

251
00:14:30,270 --> 00:14:32,320
I won't break off the engagement because of this.

252
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:33,480
I knew it.

253
00:14:34,550 --> 00:14:35,240
All right.

254
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:36,480
Here.

255
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:38,720
Take this.

256
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:39,780
What are you doing?

257
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,640
The Earth follows the laws.

258
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:44,080
The essences of Yin and Yang are combined.

259
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,550
Carry out all the laws and principles.

260
00:14:45,550 --> 00:14:46,670
Yin and Yang are just like a mirror.

261
00:14:46,670 --> 00:14:47,480
True forms swiftly appear.

262
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:48,120
Appear quickly in your real shapes.

263
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:49,050
Close your eyes.

264
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:50,850
What... What are you doing?

265
00:14:53,870 --> 00:14:54,270
Banxia,

266
00:14:54,270 --> 00:14:56,380
I... I know I'm a good man.

267
00:14:56,670 --> 00:14:57,200
But...

268
00:14:57,670 --> 00:14:59,200
We can't do this now.

269
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,470
-B-Because...
-Take it.

270
00:15:00,470 --> 00:15:01,700
There should be a certain degree of propriety in the interaction between men and women.

271
00:15:01,700 --> 00:15:03,080
And you haven't officially married into my family yet.

272
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:04,010
Shut your mouth.

273
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:08,030
Okay.

274
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:17,780
Banxia!

275
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:19,290
Spicy, spicy, so spicy!

276
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,480
Hang in there for a bit. Hang in there for a bit.

277
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:22,200
Open your eyes, open your eyes, open your eyes.

278
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:22,750
Look, look, look.

279
00:15:22,750 --> 00:15:24,080
Look there, look there.

280
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:30,170
Look at what?

281
00:15:31,750 --> 00:15:32,390
Nothing?

282
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:33,670
What?

283
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:38,480
The dosage isn't enough.

284
00:15:39,320 --> 00:15:41,050
Wait a moment. Let's try again.

285
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:42,390
Banxia.

286
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:43,390
Banxia, I...

287
00:15:43,390 --> 00:15:44,150
Hold this, hold this.

288
00:15:44,150 --> 00:15:44,670
Banxia.

289
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:45,600
The Earth follows the laws.

290
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:46,390
I... I don't know

