00:39:41,400 --> 00:39:42,220
To deal with matters involving demons,

871
00:39:42,220 --> 00:39:43,710
I must certainly find Xuanye.

872
00:39:43,710 --> 00:39:46,150
Ordinary clinics can't deal with these matters.

873
00:39:46,150 --> 00:39:46,690
Moreover,

874
00:39:46,690 --> 00:39:48,070
if I had sent her back to Shendu

875
00:39:48,070 --> 00:39:49,590
and that demon had come after her,

876
00:39:49,590 --> 00:39:51,720
how would I be supposed to deal with it?

877
00:39:53,720 --> 00:39:54,670
Right.

878
00:39:55,750 --> 00:39:56,710
I didn't realize

879
00:39:56,840 --> 00:39:58,170
you were so thoughtful.

880
00:39:59,150 --> 00:40:00,000
Am I?

881
00:40:08,650 --> 00:40:10,720
I used the insect oil Youhuang gave me.

882
00:40:10,720 --> 00:40:11,870
I intended to lure the demon away

883
00:40:11,870 --> 00:40:12,880
and capture it in one fell swoop.

884
00:40:12,880 --> 00:40:13,810
But in the end...

885
00:40:15,440 --> 00:40:16,840
It turned out as you saw.

886
00:40:17,550 --> 00:40:18,750
I underestimated it.

887
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:21,610
What happened next?

888
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:23,400
Later, he recognized the insect oil.

889
00:40:23,400 --> 00:40:25,000
So he guessed that I knew you.

890
00:40:25,130 --> 00:40:26,090
He then tried every possible way

891
00:40:26,090 --> 00:40:28,290
to force me to reveal your whereabouts.

892
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:30,840
He's after you.

893
00:40:32,340 --> 00:40:33,920
I've brought trouble upon you.

894
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:34,550
I'm sorry.

895
00:40:34,840 --> 00:40:36,280
What do you mean by trouble?

896
00:40:36,280 --> 00:40:37,480
You saved my life.

897
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:38,490
Besides,

898
00:40:38,590 --> 00:40:40,720
didn't you also save Youhuang's life?

899
00:40:44,240 --> 00:40:46,770
I'll resolve this matter as soon as possible.

900
00:40:47,870 --> 00:40:49,470
But you must be very careful.

901
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:51,190
That demon is powerful.

902
00:40:51,960 --> 00:40:53,560
He's difficult to deal with.

903
00:40:54,280 --> 00:40:55,030
I know.

904
00:40:56,480 --> 00:40:58,340
I know you're used to being alone,

905
00:40:58,480 --> 00:40:59,480
but there are some things

906
00:40:59,480 --> 00:41:01,180
you shouldn't try to handle all by yourself.

907
00:41:01,180 --> 00:41:02,580
If you can't handle this,

908
00:41:03,180 --> 00:41:04,360
I can ask people from the government office

909
00:41:04,360 --> 00:41:05,000
to help.

910
00:41:06,800 --> 00:41:08,360
I appreciate your kindness,

911
00:41:08,360 --> 00:41:09,280
but that won't be necessary.

912
00:41:09,280 --> 00:41:09,840
Alright.

913
00:41:10,210 --> 00:41:11,540
Given what you said,

914
00:41:11,980 --> 00:41:12,800
you must have acknowledged

915
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:13,840
this favor.

916
00:41:14,710 --> 00:41:15,770
So, can you help me?

917
00:41:20,190 --> 00:41:20,710
Come in.

918
00:41:27,360 --> 00:41:28,000
How is she?

919
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:30,550
She was poisoned by demon poison.

920
00:41:30,550 --> 00:41:32,040
She needs someone with strong Yang energy

921
00:41:32,040 --> 00:41:33,790
to take care of her closely for 21 days.

922
00:41:33,790 --> 00:41:35,630
Only then can the poison be neutralized.

923
00:41:35,630 --> 00:41:37,590
It's best not to leave her side at all,

924
00:41:37,590 --> 00:41:39,450
whether you eat, drink, or sleep.

925
00:41:40,800 --> 00:41:42,860
I have to be with her even when I sleep?

926
00:41:42,880 --> 00:41:44,080
Is there such poison?

927
00:41:44,710 --> 00:41:45,440
Yes, indeed.

928
00:41:45,710 --> 00:41:47,190
I only learned about it

929
00:41:47,190 --> 00:41:48,360
after I met her.

930
00:41:49,190 --> 00:41:50,150
Aren't there other ways

931
00:41:50,150 --> 00:41:50,900
to neutralize the poison?

932
00:41:50,900 --> 00:41:51,840
No, there aren't.

933
00:41:51,840 --> 00:41:52,400
It's not convenient to take care of her

934
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:53,360
in my place.

935
00:41:53,550 --> 00:41:54,950
You should take her home.

936
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:57,480
Me?

937
00:41:58,000 --> 00:41:58,760
Didn't I tell you?

938
00:41:58,760 --> 00:41:59,210
It's not convenient to take care of her

939
00:41:59,210 --> 00:41:59,940
in my place.

940
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:00,960
Come on.

941
00:42:14,550 --> 00:42:15,230
Thank you.

942
00:42:38,800 --> 00:42:40,030
Can I really do it?

943
00:42:41,640 --> 00:42:42,570
If you don't try,

944
00:42:43,400 --> 00:42:45,330
how can you know it's not possible?

945
00:42:59,190 --> 00:42:59,790
Remember,

946
00:43:00,070 --> 00:43:02,000
the magic spell can only last for two hours.

947
00:43:02,000 --> 00:43:03,800
Be careful in everything you do.

948
00:43:07,640 --> 00:43:08,160
Mr. Bai,

949
00:43:08,440 --> 00:43:09,840
you've come early today.

950
00:43:11,000 --> 00:43:11,660
Hello, Sir.

951
00:43:12,110 --> 00:43:12,800
Please.

952
00:43:50,230 --> 00:43:51,510
Mr. Bai's Qin skills are truly amazing.

953
00:43:51,510 --> 00:43:53,030
They make people feel as if they are in a fairyland

954
00:43:53,030 --> 00:43:54,800
and completely immersed in the music.

955
00:43:54,800 --> 00:43:55,230
Great!

956
00:43:55,590 --> 00:43:57,000
Great!

957
00:43:57,320 --> 00:44:00,960
Great! Great! Great!
